<!-- Rama sin deuda: mensaje de felicitación -->
<section class="step" data-step="step-nuevo-3B" aria-label="¡Eso es genial!" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-10 px-6 pb-8 max-md:pb-[120px] max-md:pt-12 max-md:px-3 max-[360px]:pt-7 max-[360px]:px-5 gap-0">
    <!-- Título -->
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-[clamp(19px,5.2vw,36px)] text-navy text-center tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.15] max-md:leading-[1.1] max-w-[600px] whitespace-nowrap max-md:mt-8">
      <span class="text-amber">Libérate</span> del estrés financiero
    </h1>
    <!-- Pablo + burbuja -->
    <div class="flex-1 max-md:flex-none flex items-center justify-center relative w-full max-w-[480px] py-6 max-md:py-[40px] max-md:h-[260px] mt-6 max-md:mt-4">
      <div
        class="absolute top-[30%] right-0 md:-right-[40px] bg-white px-[18px] py-[10px] max-[360px]:px-[14px] max-[360px]:py-2 rounded-[var(--radius-md)] rounded-bl-[4px] shadow-clay-card font-display font-bold text-[13px] md:text-[15px] text-navy z-5 -translate-y-[120%] max-md:-translate-y-[60%] animate-[bubbleSlide_500ms_var(--ease-clay)_500ms_backwards] max-w-[220px]"
        aria-live="polite"
      >
        ¡Eso es genial, te felicito! Eso te permite crecer tus ahorros aún más rápido. Siempre
        deberías buscar pagar préstamos caros lo más pronto posible.
      </div>
      <div class="w-[300px] h-[320px] md:w-[350px] md:h-[350px] max-[360px]:w-[260px] max-[360px]:h-[260px] mt-16 max-md:translate-y-[100px] pablo-hero">
        <img
          src="/onboarding/images/pablo/pablo-point.png"
          alt="Pablo"
          width="350"
          height="350"
          loading="lazy"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover scale-170"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-[14px] w-full max-md:mt-[200px] relative z-10">
      <button class="btn-primary btn-primary--compact" onclick="pabloNext()">
        Siguiente
        <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
